$$\Delta_k=\mbox{Van}(1,...,k-1,0,k+1,...,n)=(-1)^{k+1}\left|
\begin{array}{cccccc}
1&\ldots&k-1&k+1&\ldots&n\\
1& &(k-1)^2&(k+1)^2& &n^2\\
\vdots& &\vdots&\vdots& &\vdots\\
 & & & & & \\
\vdots& &\vdots&\vdots& &\vdots\\
